			<node ID="ID_513483849" TEXT="This article is an introduction to clustering and its types. K-means clustering  Hierarchical clustering have been explained in details.  An Introduction to Clustering and different methods of clustering.  Overview. Clustering is the task of dividing the population or data points into a number of groups such that data points in the same " />
