			<node ID="ID_475103457" TEXT="2.3. Clustering&#182;. Clustering of unlabeled data can be performed with the module sklearn.cluster.. Each clustering algorithm comes in two variants: a class that implements the fit method to learn the clusters on train data and a function that given train data returns an array of integer labels corresponding to the different clusters. For the class the labels over the training data can be " />
